    • chooseResources

      public void chooseResources​(Game game, Player player, Map<Shelf,​Map<ResourceType,​Integer>> shelves) throws CannotChooseException, IllegalResourceTransactionReplacementsException, IllegalResourceTransactionContainersException, IllegalResourceTransferException
      Chooses the initial resources to be given to the player.
      Parameters:
      game - the game the player is playing in
      player - the player
      shelves - the destination shelves
      Throws:
      CannotChooseException - all the allowed initial resources have already been chosen
      IllegalResourceTransactionReplacementsException
      IllegalResourceTransactionContainersException
      IllegalResourceTransferException - when trasferring resources to a container fails
